metadata.name: A Break in the Pattern
metadata.description:
"A Break In The Pattern" 



Melbourne has an abundance of intriguing architectural styles. On the edge of the CBD, you can find the RMIT Design Hub Gallery. A beautifully memorising building dedicated to finding out the role of design in the world today. 

Having a deep love for architecture, I often found myself gravitating toward this end of town, infatuated by its presence.
